de.adorsys.datasafe.metainfo.version.api.version

Interface EncryptedLatestLinkService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EncryptedLatestLinkServiceImpl, EncryptedLatestLinkServiceImplRuntimeDelegatable

    public interface EncryptedLatestLinkService
    Manages `latest` file version link location and provides capability to read its path. For example it can be managed using RDBMS.
